1) install:
- build node-base, python-base, import & crossbar

2) start-env: (ok)
- start crossbar

3) import: (can be done anytime & several times between 2 & 8)
- start/stop/rm import image

4) build: (ok)
- build encoder (+trainer), classifier (+trainer), matcher, controller

5) start:
- start containers of images of step 4 (with volumes & links)

5.1) run-test
5.2) clean-test

6) stop:
- stop & rm containers of step 5 (& rm volumes)

7) unbuild: (ok)
- rm images of step 4

8) stop-env: (ok)
- stop & rm containers of step 3 (& rm volumes)

9) uninstall: (ok)
- rm images of step 1
